This summer we are staying ✨FAB✨ with making sure we take care of our sexual health!  Here are some ways to stay informed!: 

1. Planned Parenthood of Illinois is here to make sure you have a safe and enjoyable summer with their wide range of services. Learn more at ppil.org.

2. Nothing is sexier than practicing safe sex! Planned Parenthood of Illinois is here to make sure you can live your best life, including your best sex life. Get the care you need at ppil.org. 

3. Safe sex is self care. Visit Planned Parenthood of Illinois to get the information and resources you need to stay on top of your sexual health. Get started at ppil.org.
